content.rendered:
Directed by Nagesh Kukunoor.

Written by Nagesh Kukunoor.

Cast Krrish Chhabria(Chotu). Hetal Gada(Pari). Vipin Sharma(Dungaram). Gulfam Khan(Gowri). Idhant Singh(Madan Mohan). Swastik Ram Chavan(Bully (as Swastik Chavan)). Narendar Singh Rajpurohit(Bathposh). Vincent Daniel(Post-Master). Harmeet Arora(Aashaji). Sanjana Singh(Phoolan). Rajiv Laxman(Gardu). Rishi Deshpande(Truck driver). Vijay Maurya(Drunk man). Pratyaksh Kalra(Samsher Singh). Subramani Ramachandran(Jeep passenger (as Subramani R.)). Chiranjeet Chhabria(Jeep Driver). Rahul Lohani(Saffron Robed Man). Kelash Daangi(Bus conductor). Maan Singh Meena(Police man). Vibha Chhibber(Sheera Mata). Chet Dixon(Douglas Adams). Ramakant Dayma(Old-Man). Flora Saini(Gypsy Woman). Bharti Achrekar(Dadisa). Suresh Menon(Badrinath). Abbas Syed(Mechanic (as Abbas Sayyad)). Rohit Shilwant(Cripple). Ninad Kamat(Aatmaram Khandelwal). Vipin Bhati(Doctor). Asha Pareek(Eye Doctor)

Languages Hindi. Rajasthani. English.

Producers Shiladitya Bora. Elahe Hiptoola. Nagesh Kukunoor. Manish Mundra.

Production Kukunoor Movies. Manish Realities.
